    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "(Parliament rejected the request)\nSo the agenda is unchanged.\nWe move now to a request by the ESN Group â for Wednesday as well â which has requested that a Commission statement on 'Presidential elections in Romania, particularly the Constitutional Court's ruling of 8Â March' be added as the second point in the afternoon.\nI give the floor toÂ Christine Anderson to move the request."
