      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_1"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "But I still believe that there are enough Commission officials listening to this broadcast anyway. And I think that this House should not be stuck because of this.\nSo I would like to give the floor to Tomas TobÃ© to open the debate."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-10T18:00:53"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_191",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_191"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_139"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "O objetivo Ã© que possamos garantir que as geraÃ§Ãµes futuras tenham acesso a Ã¡gua para consumo e tambÃ©m para as vÃ¡rias atividades econÃ³micas, particularmente a agricultura.\nO sul da Europa e, particularmente, Portugal sofrem atualmente uma elevada escassez de Ã¡gua. No nosso caso, as regiÃµes do Alentejo e do Algarve sÃ£o as mais afetadas.\nPortugal apresentou ontem a EstratÃ©gia Nacional para a GestÃ£o da Ãgua, que tem por nome Â«Ãgua que uneÂ», que prevÃª resolver a escassez de Ã¡gua, quer para consumo humano quer para outras utilizaÃ§Ãµes. EstÃ¡ previsto um investimento de mais de 5Â milÂ milhÃµes de euros.Â Por isso, espero que a UniÃ£o Europeia seja solidÃ¡ria, que assuma as suas responsabilidades e que ajude os Estados-Membros.\nÃgua Ã© vida nos territÃ³rios, Ã¡gua Ã© coesÃ£o social, Ã¡gua Ã© economia, Ã¡gua Ã© seguranÃ§a. Sim, falo da Ã¡gua e da Ã¡gua que nos une na UniÃ£o Europeia."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-10T21:54:50"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_146",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_146"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_113"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "We must bolster Moldova's resilience now. This is about more than financial aid. It is about resilience, reforms and Moldova's EU path. Strengthening institutions, independent media and electoral integrity must be immediate, not gradual.\nThe first payout is set at 20Â %, but in this critical moment, that's not enough. We should amend the plan and increase it by an additional 5Â %. Moving faster and further sends a clear message: Moldova belongs in Europe, free from malign influence."
      }
    ],
