      {
        "@value": "Eva Maydell"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_35",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "participant_35"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#isAffiliatedWith": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_PPE"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#name": [
      {
        "@value": "Tomas TobÃ©"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_49",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_49"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_27"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Because of that reckless attitude, we, the Europeans are in huge danger. EU is losing the international race. China and US are growing faster, more stable and more innovative. Many nations are mocking the EU with such excessive bureaucracy. Our continent has become a sick man of the world.\nWe urgently need to deregulate our economy, we have to break the chains that hinder our growth. The Commission is proposing the Omnibus package. It is a step in the right direction, but it's a very small step. It's not enough. The Omnibus initiative is shallow. You are trying to avoid making â Madam is absent, of course â you are trying to avoid making hard decisions.\nWe need new deregulations with which we shout: cut, cut, cut and, once again, cut. We have to throw a lot of directives into trash where they belong. There is a lot of work ahead of us to get rid of the unnecessary burdens from our economy. The Omnibus proposal needs to be amended and extended."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-10T18:09:06"
      }
    ]
  },
