        "@value": "SunÄana Glavak"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_103",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_103"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_74"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Right-wing politics gave us the banking and economic crash, the climate crisis, the rise of homophobia and racism and the vaccine hesitancy that cost lives. It is right-wing policies that fuel homelessness and lead to poorer pay, more discrimination and unsafe work environments. And it is the politics of the right that pours petrol on the conflicts in Ukraine and Gaza.\nSo we must greet the promotion of 'simplification' and 'cutting red tape' with deep suspicion. Our environmental and social standards were hard fought for. We cannot allow the rest of this Parliament to be driven by a deregulation agenda.\nThe market has no conscience â neither, it seems, do those who worship it."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-10T19:37:17"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_98",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "contribution_98"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#madeBy": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_69"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "Maar er zijn ook best wel vragen te stellen bij deze voorstellen. Hoe denkt de Commissie bijvoorbeeld misstanden als kinderarbeid en slavernij te bestrijden als bedrijven niet langer verder hoeven te kijken dan hun directe zakenrelaties? We willen graag een verduidelijking van dit specifieke punt.\nOndertussen roep ik de Commissie op om ook andere wetgeving onder handen te nemen. Denk aan de eveneens doorgeslagen natuurherstelwet en de sterk verouderde nitraatrichtlijn: wetgeving die met name het agrarisch bedrijfsleven heel wat hoofdbrekens kost. Deze vereenvoudigingsoperatie mag niet beperkt blijven tot de voorstellen die nu voorliggen."
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#timestamp": [
      {
        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime",
        "@value": "2025-03-10T19:29:29"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/madrid_proposal_19",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#hasTopic": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/madrid_topic_19"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#identifier": [
      {
        "@value": "madrid_proposal_19"
      }
    ],
    "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#text": [
      {
        "@value": "El centro turístico y comercial de Madrid está sólo a 700 metros de la Casa de Campo y de Madrid Rio, pero las conexiones a él son terribles. Propongo unirlo con calles peatonales y arboladas."
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/creitem11",
    "@type": [
      "https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Topic"
